# Skills Discovery

When task intent matches, prefer loading skills from:

1. `.agents/skills/*/SKILL.md`
2. `.claude/skills/*/SKILL.md`
3. `.github/skills/*/SKILL.md`

If multiple skills match, choose the smallest set that covers the task.

For generation/scaffolding tasks, prioritize:

- `.agents/skills/module-conventions-generator/SKILL.md`
